      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a project or a source for parts. The exterior has significant cosmetic issues, including several large dents, heavy paint oxidation, and some visible rust spots along the wheel wells. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with multiple tears and deep stains, and several interior trim pieces are missing or broken. Mechanically, the car requires immediate attention; it has a rough idle, several fluid leaks, and the suspension is very loose. While it currently starts, it is not recommended for long-distance driving without major repairs.",
