    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained by its previous owners. The engine starts up without hesitation and runs smoothly, while the transmission provides reliable shifting through all gears. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-preserved, showing only minor signs of regular use. The exterior paint retains a nice shine, though you may find a few small, typical road chips upon close inspection. Overall, this is a dependable and high-performing car that is ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
