      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exceptional vehicle, maintained to an uncompromising standard of excellence. This specimen represents the pinnacle of its class, boasting a flawless exterior and a cabin that retains its original factory luster. Every detail has been meticulously preserved, offering the discerning driver a like-new experience. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle in truly pristine, showroom condition.",
